Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:02.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你一定要聽仔細
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從現在開始要對你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是一件非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:12.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我們即將開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:15.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}代代相傳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:17.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}永不停息的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:21.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個很長很長的… 旅途的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:33.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}肚子餓了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:35.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:36.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從剛才開始你就一直在叫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.02,0:00:39.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}走的太慢了  你再走快點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:40.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  我說你們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:45.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們知道拉麵套餐是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.99,0:00:48.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大哥哥現在餓極了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:50.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}無論如何都很想吃拉麵套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:53.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但遺憾的是我身無分文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:54.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:58.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來來  精彩的人偶劇表演就要開始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:00.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}覺得有趣再付錢喲～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:08.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:08.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:12.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}厲害吧～  有趣吧～  高興吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:15.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼玩意啊這是  一個髒兮兮的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:16.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好醜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:18.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}它不會些別的什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:19.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘿～  嘿～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:21.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小孩子一定要誠實…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用客套了  付錢給我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:27.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我實話實說了啊  它很醜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:30.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看這種無聊的表演會有人想付錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:31.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}傻子吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:33.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們這些小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:38.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大家跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！  拉…拉麵套餐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:01.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:05.53,AIR Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,760)}微 風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:10.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這傢伙想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:19.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}幹什麼  她想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}錢嗎  要錢我可沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:23.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不口渴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:24.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我去買飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:44.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}辛苦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:47.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎…嘎哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:56.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}黏稠濃厚  純正蜜桃味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:02.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～  哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼要這樣做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在耍我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個很好喝的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為想去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:29.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}昨天  小孩子們在海邊玩來的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:34.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那一定很有趣吧  我也好想去玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在熟睡的你的旁邊我這樣想來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:37.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從昨天起你一直在睡覺是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我用手指戳過你想把你叫醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:45.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可是卻怎麼也叫不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:47.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是我肚子餓的動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:49.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你要去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:50.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:51.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:52.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}人偶表演…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:55.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:57.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:58.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那東西真的那麼重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是謀生工具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}熱吧  不用你管了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:10.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:18.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}烏鴉～  烏鴉～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼追烏鴉去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太好了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}多虧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣我們就可以去玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼從剛才起一直纏著我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為我想去海邊玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}追逐跑啦  打水仗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:39.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後  臨別時說明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}大家揮手道別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:44.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你說的簡直就像相識已久的朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:46.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對  是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:49.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:50.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:57.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們可是彼此連名字都不知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是神尾觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:06:59.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:01.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}國崎往人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:04.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不對！  我還要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:09.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  肚子餓了  得去掙錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.55,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}於是在食物的引誘下  我厚著臉皮來到了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:19.36,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}兩個人一起吃飯的感覺真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.08,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你總是一個人吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:23.70,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽回來得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.32,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}爸爸又不在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.83,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吃完後我們去玩喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:32.58,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不行  天黑後就不好解決住宿的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.33,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還沒找到住宿的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.85,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  反正到頭來也是露宿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.31,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}住在我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.18,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我說  我們可是今天才剛剛認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:48.59,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}何況還是個來歷不明  稟性不知的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.43,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這種人你能收留麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:53.53,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}首先  你的媽媽就不會答應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.70,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽總是吊兒郎當的  我想不會在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:01.19,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…似乎不該這樣說自己的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.66,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過留下來沒有關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:06.47,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我累了  沒力氣和你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:09.22,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就明天再玩也不遲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.90,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}放暑假了嘛  有的是時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:12.77,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:14.88,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎…嘎哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:23.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你說  數學有什麼用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:26.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}二次函數什麼的  將來會有用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:26.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我怎麼知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:30.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}話說回來我為什麼要幫你做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  眼睛靠的太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:35.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  往人說話像媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:36.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:38.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是媽媽回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:49.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:51.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是她開摩托車撞到倉庫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒事  她總是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我留下來真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  我會好好說服她的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:08:59.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不准！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和你說的不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:07.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼可能讓你這個年輕男子留宿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎… 嘎哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:09.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不是說了不許再說那口頭禪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你和觀鈴是什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.88,AIR Card,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,510)\fad(1000,0)}同  班  同  學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:19.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…  同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:22.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈？  不覺得年紀大了點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.64,AIR Card,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,520)\fad(1000,0)}不要迷上我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要迷上我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}迷你個頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}膽子倒是不小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這點我倒不討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  往人是大好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:37.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:38.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就讓你住下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:39.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的真的  自然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過有兩個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要睡在倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:50.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}陪我喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:56.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後那個男人最後這樣說道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最終被迷上了的…  可能是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:04.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼樣  是我贏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後我就回了他一句
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:08.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你放走的那條是美人魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼樣  這招管用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她怎麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽正在興頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:19.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我說吃閒飯的  怎麼一副無精打采的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不表演點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  往人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}表演…  你要讓我表演什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:31.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}色情告白也好  絕活表演也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:33.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:38.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是剛才的那個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就是靠這表演來賺錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的母親也曾經是以此維持生計的旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這難道不無聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:57.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你根本沒有表演的天份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過很棒是吧  沒用任何障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}和那沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:08.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算用繩子吊著  只要有意思就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:09.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}睡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  都已經要自己去倉庫睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:16.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈哈哈  其實沒有表演才能也沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喝酒忘掉它  喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我叫晴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:23.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神尾晴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}再給我一杯  阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:29.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就是不願意讓你這麼叫才告訴你名字的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是個不懂事的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那麼  你是離家出走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:41.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是在追尋目標或是自己的夢想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:42.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是年輕人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}的確是比你年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你挺有意思的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:52.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:55.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看男人的眼光還是有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓你在這兒住一段時間也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:59.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過有事拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能不能幫我照看這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:03.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這孩子有時做事讓人不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:07.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}毛毛躁躁的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看到好玩的東西想都不想就衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓我做保姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:16.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還有  能不能幫忙讓她改掉那口頭禪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:18.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個「嘎哦」啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每當為難或是想哭的時候總是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是在學恐龍的叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這孩子非常喜歡恐龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是她小時候就有的口頭禪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:32.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這孩子  到現在也依然長不大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼  你不是放暑假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  我其實是參加補習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晴子已經出門了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:52.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  她每天早上很早就走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:55.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很久沒有和別人一起吃早飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人今天有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}先把你送到學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是晴子拜託我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:06.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說讓我看著你不許你冒傻氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎  說的我簡直沒信用可言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}畫好了  這個城鎮的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:15.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你畫的好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:19.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有了這個就應該可以知道人多的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以為你的工作做參考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:24.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小觀鈴陷入危機了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到時候我來接你一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就在這裏集合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}V
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:51.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！  這是…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:54.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這就是那傢伙的內心世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:00.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:02.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:06.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是這小鎮特產的傳說中的生物？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:09.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真要是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}像童話中那樣給它點恩惠的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}應該可以期待著它的回報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:16.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好  到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:17.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給你看些好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:23.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:27.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看了這麼精彩的表演後不禁想要回報我些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:31.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:33.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:54.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}覺悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你這個邪惡的宇宙生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊──
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:17.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不明外星生物搶跑了我的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:19.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是說它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}土豆可不是外星生物喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:25.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我家附近的流浪狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:27.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這傢伙  果然是狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的是又給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:40.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你為什麼道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:44.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為土豆說是它把人偶叼到了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看樣子是想和你玩來著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你聽得懂它的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  我們是好朋友喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吧  土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:57.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看來世界上還是有我不知道的天地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:00.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:03.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:06.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不行  還是要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是霧島佳乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:16.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:17.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}國崎往人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}莫非  你很閒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:20.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:21.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:25.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在任命你為空閒空閒星人2號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:26.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}誰是1號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:28.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然后土豆是3號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那空閒空閒星人都幹些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就只是閒著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這就是空閒空閒星人的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吧  真閒啊  土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我得去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以就在這裏拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:50.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不是空閒空閒星人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那種話你也信啊  真是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:56.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:17:00.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}穿那種校服的都是些不正常的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:02.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:05.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:09.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有沒有想過如果可以使用魔法的話會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:12.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:15.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吃驚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}魔法…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  往人～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}錢賺的怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:35.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一本萬利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇～  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:39.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對不起  騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:44.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不找個更熱鬧的地方是賺不到錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:48.81,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可為什麼下班時間的車站卻如此清閒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:52.03,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為這條鐵路已經被廢棄了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.64,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼不早說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:55.28,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘎… 嘎哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:56.83,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.39,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼要打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:01.84,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是晴子說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:05.09,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說看到你說口頭禪時就要提醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.19,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好可愛啊  呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.02,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是遠野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.17,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:17.07,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:22.21,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在緊張什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.80,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:28.87,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.24,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.72,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是… 是啊  真的很巧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.47,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  吃了一驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.97,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.95,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}日光浴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.51,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}開玩笑的  現在是傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:48.48,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  她是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:49.99,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}遠野美風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.60,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:52.92,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}非常聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:56.10,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}成績年級第一  還是天文部的部長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:19:00.78,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請盡量叫我遠野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.58,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂～  美風～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.31,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！  往人像落葉一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.93,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快呀快呀  咱們繼續吹泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.51,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在的小滿可是巔峰狀態喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:19.10,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:21.55,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個女孩是你的妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.31,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:25.26,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小滿是美風的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.72,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這位姐姐是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:29.08,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是遠野的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.43,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很─疼─的─
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.89,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是誰  你也是美風的同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.23,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是被你撞飛的善良的路人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.48,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎喲～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:43.48,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我知道了  美風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:46.50,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這傢伙是來抓我們的變態人販子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:48.29,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  我也是被抓目標…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}誰是人販子！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.51,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不好  這傢伙興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.55,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}少女的危機呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:56.86,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  好大的聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.34,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神尾同學  他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:01.76,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這位是國崎往人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:05.08,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是一位旅人  現在暫住在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.56,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}旅人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:10.44,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}身為人販子還沒有住的地方  你真是無藥可救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.19,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…神尾同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:27.23,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們差不多也該回去了…
